00:20:59.890 --> 00:21:04.260
blah, blah". But now I understand it's very
important to

00:21:04.260 --> 00:21:08.051
always follow what you feel. And so, I think
that's why.

00:21:08.051 --> 00:21:11.680
I think the audience is very strong; there
is that and there is the power of

00:21:11.680 --> 00:21:15.731
recommendation. I mean, for a brand. When
