00:22:22.470 --> 00:22:23.470
I.

00:22:23.470 --> 00:22:25.049
&gt;&gt; Presenter: Some people cannot handle that
kind of traffic.

00:22:25.049 --> 00:22:29.120
&gt;&gt; Garance: Yeah exactly. You're like ha -- maybe
