00:24:37.200 --> 00:24:42.311
easy to stray and go in the wrong direction.

00:24:42.311 --> 00:24:45.600
&gt;&gt;Presenter: And so, how does that contrast
with when you're hired

00:24:45.600 --> 00:24:48.720
by an advertiser or, let's say, by a magazine
