00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:51.950
content from them. How do you maintain that
voice that

00:24:51.950 --> 00:24:54.670
people know you for but still fulfill that.

00:24:54.670 --> 00:24:58.960
&gt;&gt;Garance: I always try to have a conversation.
And then

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:01.690
understand I'm very happy now that, if I don't
feel

00:25:01.690 --> 00:25:06.370
something, I'm have the luxury of not doing
it. It's a

00:25:06.370 --> 00:25:09.190
choice. You know, so I don't really care about
making

00:25:09.190 --> 00:25:12.850
amounts of super-great money. I feel like
what I have

00:25:12.850 --> 00:25:17.010
right now is wonderful. I think I'm more happy
expressing myself and taking pictures and

00:25:17.010 --> 00:25:21.990
illustrating
than having stuff. So, you know, I'm also

00:25:21.990 --> 00:25:25.120
-- I can say
no. It doesn't weigh on me. I don't have to

00:25:25.120 --> 00:25:29.960
-- so, but
I try to have a conversation and see what

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:33.440
would be smart.
